#ROOM
Vnum     41700
Name     &rThe Entrance to the Molten Core&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The narrow ledge of the Searing Gorge falls away into a massive, 
vertical shaft of fire and smoke. You stand on the threshold of 
the Molten Core, the deepest prison of the Firelord. The air is 
so hot it blisters the skin, and the ground vibrates with the 
heartbeat of the mountain. A shimmering, white-hot portal 
glows within the mouth of the cave.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    36562
Desc      Return to the Window of the Core in Searing Gorge.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41701
Desc      The path into the deep fire.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41701
Name     &rThe Magma Thoroughfare&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide thoroughfare carved from solid basalt. The walls are 
streaked with veins of glowing iron, and the ceiling is lost 
in a haze of thick, sulfurous smoke. Molten giants stand like 
statues in alcoves along the path, their eyes tracking your 
every movement.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41700
Desc      The entrance portal.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41702
Desc      The intersection of ash.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41510 10 41701
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41702
Name     &rThe Intersection of Ash&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The main road splits here into three distinct paths. To the 
west, the air is thick with the scent of wet fur and raw 
meat. To the east, the sound of rhythmic chanting echoes 
from a high stone hall. To the north, the road leads deeper 
into the volcanic heart.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41701
Desc      The entry thoroughfare.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    41703
Desc      Toward the Magmadar Den.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    41720
Desc      Toward the Flamewaker Quarter.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41750
Desc      Toward the Hall of the Firelord.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41511 5 41702
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41703
Name     &rThe Magmadar Den - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls here are covered in thick, black hair and bits of 
charred bone. The sound of deep, rhythmic snoring causes the 
stone floor to vibrate. Lucifron can be seen slithering 
between the massive pillars ahead.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    41702
Desc      The intersection.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41704
Desc      The Lair of Lucifron.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41502 1 41703
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41704
Name     &rThe Lair of Lucifron&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide circular hall filled with the shadow of the mountain. 
Lucifron stands before a large obsidian altar, his curved 
blade reflecting the orange glow of the nearby lava pits. 
His loyal guards hiss in anticipation.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41703
Desc      The den entry.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41705
Desc      The Lair of Magmadar.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41502 1 41704
  Reset G 1 41606 1
Reset M 0 41514 5 41704
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41705
Name     &rThe Lair of Magmadar&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The highest point of the southern dens. The massive core hound 
Magmadar sleeps upon a bed of cooling lava, his three heads 
shifting in his sleep. The air is stagnant and reeks of 
reptile musk and smoke.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41704
Desc      Lucifron's lair.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41503 1 41705
  Reset G 1 41603 1
  Reset G 1 41611 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41720
Name     &rThe Flamewaker Quarter - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The architecture here is more refined, with pillars carved in the 
image of serpents. Firelords hover near the ceiling, summoning 
minor elementals to patrol the halls.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    41702
