#ROOM
Vnum     41721
Name     &rThe Hall of Gehennas&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular chamber. Gehennas stands in the center of 
a glowing ritual circle, his hands weaving a spell of 
pure shadow-fire. The walls are lined with high-ranking 
flamewaker guards.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41720
Desc      The quarter entry.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41722
Desc      Toward Garr's Enclave.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41504 1 41721
  Reset G 1 41610 1
Reset M 0 41514 5 41721
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41722
Name     &rGarr's Enclave - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air here is heavy and still. The ground is composed of 
thousands of small, obsidian stones that crunch underfoot. 
A massive rock elemental can be seen standing like a mountain 
in the distance.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41721
Desc      The hall of gehennas.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    41723
Desc      The Peak of Garr.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41505 1 41722
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41723
Name     &rThe Peak of Garr&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The highest point of the eastern halls. Garr stands in the 
center of a wide stone terrace, surrounded by eight 
smaller rock elementals who hum in a low, grounding pitch.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    41722
Desc      The enclave entry.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41505 1 41723
  Reset G 1 41602 1
  Reset G 1 41613 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41750
Name     &rThe Road to the Firelord - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air becomes blistering hot as you approach the volcanic 
center. A wide road of massive pavers leads toward a 
circular loop of stone. The scent of brimstone is overwhelming.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41702
Desc      The intersection.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41751
Desc      The Searing Loop.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41513 10 41750
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41751
Name     &rThe Searing Loop - South&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A long stone path that circles a massive central pit of lava. 
Baron Geddon patrols this loop in a never-ending cycle, 
his body a pillar of pure, white-hot flame.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41750
Desc      The road entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    41752
Desc      The Searing Loop West.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    41753
Desc      The Searing Loop East.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41506 1 41751
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41752
Name     &rThe Searing Loop - West&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The western half of the loop. To the west, a high bridge 
leads toward the Shazzrah's quarters. Molten giants 
keep watch over the burning abyss.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    41751
Desc      The loop south.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    41754
Desc      Toward Shazzrah's Hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41516 5 41752
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41754
Name     &rThe Hall of Shazzrah&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A circular room filled with shimmering arcane distortion. 
Shazzrah stands in the center, his many heads muttering 
contradictory incantations. He teleports rapidly across 
the floor, leaving a trail of blue static.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    41752
Desc      The loop west.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 41507 1 41754
  Reset G 1 41618 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41753
Name     &rThe Searing Loop - East&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The eastern half of the loop. To the east, a wide thoroughfare 
leads toward Sulfuron's balcony. Lava surgers rush 
along the stone path.
~
#EXIT
