#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41755
Name     &rThe Hall of Sulfuron Harbinger&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large stone platform overlooking a river of magma. 
Sulfuron Harbinger stands in the center, surrounded by 
his elite flamewaker guards. He balances a massive 
obsidian mace, his eyes glowing with inner fire.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    41753
