#ROOM
Vnum     41800
Name     &rThe Road to the Core - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The stone path narrows as it leads into the very heart of the 
mountain. The sound of thousands of tons of falling magma 
creates a constant, low-frequency roar.
~
