#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41801
Name     &rThe Lair of Golemagg the Incinerator&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular chamber. In the center, the titanic 
molten giant Golemagg stands guard, flanked by two 
ferocious core ragers. He is the final barrier before 
the Firelord's throne.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41800
Desc      The road entry.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41810
