  Reset G 1 41619 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41810
Name     &rThe Hall of the Majordomo - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The architecture here is grand and ancient, with white marble 
statues of elementals lining the hall. The air is clear of 
smoke, but the heat is even more intense.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41801
Desc      Golemagg's lair.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
