Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular room filled with dozens of flamewaker 
guards. Majordomo Executus stands before a shimmering pool 
of molten gold, his hands raised as he prepares the 
ritual of summoning.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41810
Desc      The hall entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    41850
