Reset M 0 41514 10 41811
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41850
Name     &rThe Pit of Ragnaros&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You have reached the absolute heart of the world. A massive, 
circular pool of lava nearly five hundred feet wide sits in 
the center of the room. This is the place where the Firelord 
has slumbered since the dawn of time. The air hums with 
unfathomable power.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    41811
Desc      Return to the Majordomo's seat.~
